/article24696712.ece|title=\u2018'Geetha Govindam' review: The good guy takes over\u2019|date=16 August 2018|website=The Hindu}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2019\n|''[[N. T. R. (2018 film)|NTR Kathanayakudu]]''||[[Savitri (actress)|Savitri]]||Special appearance\n|-\n|''[[Praana]]''||Tara Anuradha|| [[Malayalam]]\n|-\n|''[[Mission Mangal]]''||| Varsha Pillai || [[Hindi ]]|| Hindi Debut \n|-\n|-\n|''[[Frozen II]]''||| Elsa || [[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| Voice Over\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"|2020\n|''[[Psycho (2019 film)|Psycho]]'' || Kamala Das IPS ||[[Tamil language|Tamil]]|| \n|-\n|style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"|''[[Kolaambi]]''||Arundhati|| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Malayalam]]||Post-Production\n|-\n|}\n\n==Web series==\n<!--Do not split this into separate article without establishing consensus through discussion-->\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n| style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\"| {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Denotes Series that have not yet been released\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-  style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! Year\n! Series\n! Role\n! Language\n! Notes\n|-\n|2020\n| ''Breathe Season 2''\n||  || [[Hindi]] ||\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Song !! Film !! Language !! Composer\n|-\n| 2010 || Payasa || [[Aidondla Aidu]]|| [[Kannada]] || Abhijit-Joe\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2011 ||Edo Anukunte|| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Ala Modalaindi]]||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Kalyani Malik]]\n|-\n| Ammammo Ammo|| [[Telugu language|Telugu]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2012 || Oh Priya Priya || [[Ishq (2012 film)|Ishq]]|| [[Telugu language|Telugu]] || [[Anoop Rubens]]\n|-\n| Payasam || [[Poppins]] || [[Malayalam language|Malayalam]] || [[Ratheesh Vegha]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"10\"|2013 || Arere Arere || [[Jabardasth (film)|Jabardasth]] || [[Telugu language|Telugu]] || [[S. Thaman]]\n|-\n| Doore Doore Neengi||[[Natholi Oru Cheriya Meenalla|Natholi Oru Cheria Meenalla]]||[[Malayalam]] || Abhijith\n|-\n| Modala Maleyante (Duet) ||[[Myna (film)|Myna]]||[[Kannada]] || Jassie Gift\n|-\n| Thu Hi Rey || [[Gunde Jaari Gallanthayyinde]]|| [[Telugu language|Telugu]] || Anoop Rubens\n|-\n| Hi my name is malini|| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Malini 22 Palayamkottai]]|| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Tamil language|Tamil]] || rowspan=\"6\"|Arvind & Shankar\n|-\n| Kanneer Thulilye (Duet)\n|-\n| Madharthamma (Immigrant Mix)\n|-\n| Hi my name is malini|| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Malini 22 Palayamkottai|Malini 22]]|| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Telugu language|Telugu]]\n|-\n| Navve Kaluva (Duet)\n|-\n|  Yennali (Immigrant Mix)\n|-\n| 2015 || Paalnilaa : Lets Do the Dandiya||[[Rockstar (2015 film)]]||[[Malayalam language|Malayalam]] || [[Prashant Pillai]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2016 || Laalijo||[[24 (2016 film)|24]]|| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| A. R. Rahman \n|-\n| Hrudayam Kannulatho||[[100 Days of Love]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.123telugu.com/mnews/100-days-of-love-to-be-dubbed-into-telugu.html|title=\u2018100 Days of Love\u2019 to be dubbed into Telugu - 123telugu.com|publisher=|accessdate=22 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/Dulquers-100-Days-of-Love-to-be-remade-in-Telugu/articleshow/51778643.cms|title=Dulquer's 100 Days of Love to be remade in Telugu \u2013 Times of India|publisher=|accessdate=22 August 2016}}</ref> || Govind Menon\n|-\n| 2018 || Va Va Vo ||[[Mohanlal (film)|Mohanlal]]||[[Malayalam language|Malayalam]] ||[[Tony Joseph Pallivathukal]]\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category\n!Film\n!Result\n|-\n|2009\n|[[Filmfare Awards South]]\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Kannada|Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Kannada]]\n|''[[Josh (2009 Kannada film)|Josh]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"9\" |2011\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Filmfare Awards South]]\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Malayalam|Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Malayalam]]\n|